 Objective 3.

 Determine if caregiver burden changes with treatment of infants and young boys with DMD.

 Preliminary data from questionnaires suggests the caregiver burden for the primary caregiver of untreated infant and young boys with DMD is minimal.

 Assessment of this with in this trial will allow us to discern if this changes with a therapeutic trial.

